gomodel:SYNGO_2249  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: TANC1 was enriched in postsynaptic density fractions.\n\n26/01/2018 Pim\n- TANC1 interacts and colocalizes with PSD-95.\n- EM data in Fig.5 is made with a pan-TANC antibody that is not gene paralog specific. This data is excluded from the referenced figures.. Experimental description: Materials and Methods\nSubcellular and PSD fractions\nSubcellular fractionations of rat brains were prepared." ;
